output.analysis:
Let's analyze this post according to our criteria:
1. Has CMF: Yes, contains "CMF11240017" 2. Refers to candidate: Yes, explicitly mentions "Marcel Ciolacu", who is one of the presidential candidates 3. Addresses wide population: Yes, it's a paid advertisement on Facebook/Instagram targeting a large audience (100,001-500,000 people) 4. Electoral objective: Yes, promotes PSD's governance program and explicitly links it to Marcel Ciolacu 5. Journalism: No, this is clearly a campaign message, not journalistic content 6. Personal opinion: No, this is an organized campaign message with official CMF number
The post describes a campaign event and promotes both parliamentary and presidential candidates. It mentions Marcel Ciolacu, who is a presidential candidate, and promotes his future actions ("le vor implementa pentru bihoreni"). This constitutes electoral propaganda for both parliamentary and presidential elections.
Given that this ad is still running after the end of the presidential campaign period (which ended at 7:00 AM on November 23rd), this constitutes a violation of Article 55 t).

conclusion.electoral-propaganda-analysis: This is clearly electoral propaganda because: - Contains official CMF number - Directly promotes a presidential candidate (Marcel Ciolacu) - Is a paid advertisement reaching a wide audience - Has clear electoral objective promoting future actions - Links the candidate to specific promises and governance programs
conclusion.message-for-police: Infomed Pro SRL, pentru incalcarea articolului 55 t) din Legea 370/2004, prin continuarea difuzării de materiale de propagandă electorală după încheierea campaniei electorale prezidențiale. Materialul promotional cu ID-ul 2094189494329421 pe facebook promovează în mod direct candidatul prezidențial Marcel Ciolacu, prin prezentarea măsurilor și propunerilor acestuia, conține număr oficial de material electoral CMF11240017, și continuă să fie difuzat ca reclamă plătită după ora 18:00 pe 23.11.2024. Materialul are obiectiv electoral explicit și se adresează publicului larg prin intermediul platformelor Facebook și Instagram.
